	$LF
	"On the first 2 tases i made from scratch a year or so ago, i was forced to do a whole lot more of weird workarounds, that would cost around 25 seconds - however by some miracle here, everything just worked out (while still crashing on most scenarios near the end of the stage, i managed to change some trajectories, jumps, and camera movement, still being able to perform optimal movement).
