	$LF
	"This level suffers from some lag on PSX, whenever 2 or more golden carrots are shown on screen, therefore i had to change movement a few times near the start of the stage to avoid slowing down too much. Merlin teaches Bugs both the "Fan" and the "Open Sesami" magic spells in this level.
